The purpose of this repository is to provide a playground to experiment with new technologies and demonstrate code.

Technologies Included:
----------------------
* ASP.Net MVC3 
* jquery
* Knockout.js
* NInject IoC
* Nhibernate (with SQLite db for simplicity)
* NUnit tests (with RhinoMocks)
* PowerShell Build scripts to setup db and build/test (using psake). 

To Build:
---------
From the command line run the following commands:

To create the database

> go db

To build and run the tests

> go

To add some test data to the database

> go populate_db


To Run:
-------

Debug the web project from Visual Studio, or run the following command line and navigate to http://localhost:8080/

> start_server